div.p:
{G22v} athāto bhūtaḍāmaramahātantrarāje °rāje] A;
                               om. G  śrīmahābhūtinīsādhanavidhivistaro
                       bhavati |

gloss.term:
A class of spirits;
                                in the Bhūta­ḍāmara Tantra this
                                term can refer to all nonhuman beings, including gods.
